                "invention-title": [
                    "Resource utilization method for stainless steel pickling solution",
                    "一种不锈钢酸洗液资源化利用的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of stainless steel pickling solution treatment processes, in particular to a stainless steel pickling solution resource utilization method which comprises the following steps: S1, mixing a stainless steel pickling solution with magnesite, and carrying out heating and oxygen introduction reaction to obtain a leaching solution and iron slag; s2, magnesium oxide is added into the leachate, and chromium precipitation residues and chromium precipitation mother liquor are obtained; s3, magnesium oxide is continuously added into the chromium precipitation mother liquor for reaction, and nickel cobalt hydroxide and nickel cobalt precipitation mother liquor are obtained through filtering; s4, hydrogen peroxide and magnesium oxide are added into the nickel and cobalt precipitation mother liquor for a reaction, and manganese residues and manganese precipitation mother liquor are obtained through filtering; and S5, adding calcium oxide into the manganese precipitation mother liquor for reaction, and filtering to obtain fluorine precipitation residues and a magnesium nitrate solution. According to the method, free acid, iron, chromium, nickel, cobalt, manganese, fluorine and other elements in the stainless steel pickling solution are subjected to segmented gradient resource utilization again, secondary pollution is not generated, no waste residues and waste gas are discharged, and the method has the advantages of being green, low in carbon, environmentally friendly and the like and has good social and economic value."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及不锈钢酸洗液处理工艺技术领域，特别涉及一种不锈钢酸洗液资源化利用的方法，包括：S1、将不锈钢酸洗液与菱镁矿混合后，进行升温通氧反应得到浸出液和铁渣；S2、向浸出液中加入氧化镁得到沉铬渣和沉铬母液；S3、向沉铬母液中继续加入氧化镁反应，过滤得到氢氧化镍钴和沉镍钴母液；S4、向沉镍钴母液中加入双氧水和氧化镁反应，过滤得到锰渣和沉锰母液；S5、向沉锰母液中加入氧化钙反应，过滤得到沉氟渣和硝酸镁溶液。本发明将不锈钢酸洗液中的游离酸、铁、铬、镍、钴、锰、氟等元素再次进行了分段梯级资源化利用，不产生二次污染，没有废渣废气排出，具有绿色低碳环保等优点和较好的社会经济价值。"
                }
            ]
